STATE EX REL. RIZVI
v.
STATE MED. BD. OF OHIO 2019-0561 Supreme Court of Ohio. June 18, 2019

CASE ANNOUNCEMENT

MISCELLANEOUS DISMISSAL

Appellant has not filed a memorandum in support of jurisdiction, due June 12, 2019, in compliance with the Rules of Practice of the Supreme Court of Ohio and therefore has failed to prosecute this cause with the requisite diligence. Cause dismissed.
